Wyndham Guise https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wyndham_Guise 0 Wyndham Guise was a British actor who appeared on stage in Edwardian musical comedies beginning in the 1890s and became a film actor during the silent era. He is sometimes credited as Windham Guise. Wyndham_Guise was a_British_actor who appeared on stage in Edwardian_musical_comedies beginning in the_1890s and became a_film_actor during the_silent_era . He is_sometimes_credited as Windham_Guise .
